      "body" : "Which version?\nWhat arguments / bitcoin.conf settings? You're sure you don't have `-gen=1` enabled?\n\nYou an try e.g. `-par=1` to reduce the number of script verification threads. By default it uses as many threads as there are cores available _minus one_, but it may be mis-estimating this.\n\nCan you find a message like this in your debug.log:\n\n```\n2015-06-29 09:35:16 Using 5 threads for script verification\n```\n",
